<div class="solution-begin"><span id='sol-start-11' class="fa-solid fa-circle-right solution-icon clickable" onclick="toggle_visibility('sol-body-11', 'sol-start-11')">  Solution </span></div><div class="solution-body" id = "sol-body-11" style="display: none;">



